#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	long long int n,q,num,min = 1000000001,max = 0;
	long long int i,j,t;
	cin >> n >> q;
	for(i=0;i<n;i++)
	{
		cin >> num;
		if(min > num)
		{
			min = num;
		}
		if(max < num)
		{
			max = num;
		}
	}
	for(i=0;i<q;i++)
	{
		cin >> t;
		if(t >= min && t<=max)
		{
			cout << "Yes";
		}
		else
			cout << "No" ;
			cout << endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
